genmean: Something that comes out of the end of a gun or gun-like object, such as a stream of water out of a water pistol, or any thing or any action directly or indirectly associated with this, especially a bullet.
verblex: 1. Of a bullet, to be fired out of a gun.
nomlex: 1. A small piece of metal with a pointed or rounded end, which is fired out of a gun. English = bullet.
